OL,6,FPolitical correspondent Lise McNally
OL,7,Freports on the latest setbacks to the
OL,8,Fplanned inquiry
OL,10,FThe national grooming gangs inquiry
OL,11,Fcontinues to cause controversy before
OL,12,Fit has even appointed a chair or heard
OL,13,Fa word of evidence.
OL,15,FA fourth survivor of grooming abuse
OL,16,Fhas resigned from the victims and
OL,17,Fsurvivors liaison panel following
OL,18,Fothers like Ellie-Ann Reynolds, from
OL,19,FBarrow.
