OL,6,FShe walked away on Monday 20 October
OL,7,Fafter sitting on the inquiry for just
OL,8,Ftwo days saying she wouldn't rejoin if
OL,9,Fher life depended on it.
OL,11,FSamantha Walker-Roberts from Oldham,
OL,12,Fis remaining on the panel, but wants
OL,13,Fthe scope of the inquiry widening to
OL,14,Fnot just include grooming gangs. She
OL,15,Fwas abducted and groomed at the age of
OL,16,F12.
OL,18,FShe fears other forms of child abuse
OL,19,Fwill be overlooked.
