OL,6,F"All victims of child abuse are equal
OL,7,Fand we all deserve a voice and we all
OL,8,Fdeserve justice".
OL,10,FThe man thought to be the only
OL,11,Fremaining candidate to chair the
OL,12,Finquiry has also withdrawn from
OL,13,Fconsideration for the role.
OL,15,FFormer police officer Jim Gamble
OL,16,Fwithdrew his name from consideration,
OL,17,Fsaying he did not feel he had a
OL,18,F"consensus of trust" among the
OL,19,Fsurvivors' group on account of his
OL,20,Fprevious profession.
