OL,3,CMore resignations and rows threaten
OL,4,Cabuse inquiry
OL,6,FGamble pointed to a "toxic
OL,7,Fenvironment" surrounding the chair's
OL,8,Fselection, and "political opportunism
OL,9,Fand point-scoring," calling it out as
OL,10,Fregrettable given the severity of the
OL,11,Finquiry's purpose.
OL,13,FHe follows Annie Hudson, a former
OL,14,Fdirector of children's services for
OL,15,FLambeth who was reported to have
OL,16,Fwithdrawn on Tuesday.
OL,18,FThe government is now left looking for
OL,19,Falternative candidates, as opposition
OL,20,Fparties call for the position to be
OL,21,Ffilled by a judge.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
