OL,6,FResponding to the news, a Home Office
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We are
OL,8,Fdisappointed that candidates to chair
OL,9,Fthat inquiry have withdrawn.
OL,11,F"This is an extremely sensitive topic,
OL,12,Fand we have to take the time to
OL,13,Fappoint the best person suitable for
OL,14,Fthe role."
OL,16,FJim Gamble was a former police officer
OL,17,Fin Northern Ireland, going on to lead
OL,18,Fthe RUC special branch in Belfast. In
OL,19,F2006, he led the Child Exploitation
OL,20,Fand Online Protection Centre, tackling
OL,21,Fonline child abuse networks.
