OL,6,FGamble said his decision was due to
OL,7,Fhis own belief that the individual
OL,8,Ftaking on the role should command the
OL,9,Fconfidence of all survivors.
OL,11,F"While I was told that the majority of
OL,12,Fthose I spoke with supported my
OL,13,Fposition, it is clear that a lack of
OL,14,Fconfidence due to my previous
OL,15,Foccupation exists among some," he said.
OL,17,F"I made a commitment that if this
OL,18,Fconsensus of trust was not present, I
OL,19,Fwould not proceed, and I must now be
OL,20,Ftrue to my word."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
