OL,6,FIn a letter published to his social
OL,7,Fmedia Gamble went on to say the
OL,8,F"highly charged and toxic environment"
OL,9,Fsurrounding the inquiry had
OL,10,F"influenced the appointment process"
OL,11,Fand impacted those close to him.
OL,13,FHis letter continued: "Regrettably,
OL,14,Fthe reaction to the appointment
OL,15,Fprocess has been defined more by the
OL,16,Fvested interests of some, as well as
OL,17,Fpolitical opportunism and point-
OL,18,Fscoring, rather than by the cross-
OL,19,Fparty consensus required to address
OL,20,Fsuch a serious national issue.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
