OL,6,F"Victims and survivors, who have been
OL,7,Flet down so often in the past, deserve
OL,8,Fbetter than to be used as leverage for
OL,9,Fshort-term gain by anyone.
OL,11,F"Moving forward, I hope they remain at
OL,12,Fthe absolute centre of this inquiry."
